{"talk":{"id":67293,"name":"Gokul Upadhyayula: The life unfolding inside your cells, revealed in 3D","description":"To understand how life works, you need to watch it in action, says bioimaging scientist Gokul Upadhyayula. Taking us down to the cellular level, he shares the work behind cutting-edge microscopes that capture and record, in three dimensions, the complex behaviors of living organisms -- from infecting cancer cells to crawling immune cells -- and what they're revealing about the dynamics of biology. Watch life unfold before your eyes with the incredible visuals in this talk.","slug":"gokul_upadhyayula_the_life_unfolding_inside_your_cells_revealed_in_3d","recorded_at":"2020-03-04 00:00:00","published_at":"2020-10-09 14:41:47","updated_at":"2021-04-09 19:33:39","viewed_count":0,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":643,"name":"TEDMED 2020"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/2eb058f71928f8dd24a8dca2e4d70c5735f13845_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/2eb058f71928f8dd24a8dca2e4d70c5735f13845_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/2eb058f71928f8dd24a8dca2e4d70c5735f13845_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/2eb058f71928f8dd24a8dca2e4d70c5735f13845_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/07b47e78d0f64604704b8740849d106374f085fd_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/GokulUpadhyayula_2020P-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":6349505,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/GokulUpadhyayula_2020P-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":17568144,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/GokulUpadhyayula_2020P-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cf